    "description": "《棋境漫游》是一系列启发自国际象棋的，原创益智策略游戏的大合集。游戏运用了多种不同的主题，想象出全新的国际象棋规则与战术。每个篇章都有独特的规则、美术风格和纯手工创作的关卡！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 体验8种独特的类国际象棋游戏;<br></li><li> 战役模式包含100+益智关卡与特别挑战;<br></li><li> 收集24种主题棋子模型;<br></li><li> 独具一格的美术与靓丽优美的透视;<br></li><li> 每日/每周挑战;<br></li><li> 在排行榜互相竞争;<br></li><li> 通过现代电子游戏学习国际象棋玩法，战术和策略;<br></li><li> 当然包括“经典国际象棋”，供您学以致用！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >众多国象世界等待探索！</h2><br>下列为《棋境漫游》中所有的原创游戏：(1) 田园生活篇 (2) 屠龙勇士篇 (3) 街头足球篇 (4) 风华浪人篇;(5) 背水一战 (6) 骑士至上 (7) 小兵狂欢 (8) 足球象棋。<br><br>来实际感受一下吧：<br><br>在<strong>屠龙勇士篇</strong>中，你需要操控兵卒到达道路的尽头，破坏龙核以消灭恐怖的巨龙。这绝非易事！每当兵卒移动时，巨龙都会吐出龙息攻击棋盘，所有未受保护的棋子都会被消灭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/a6051ac1919669c81c87d6d47afd54e9.poster.avif?t=1745518342\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/a6051ac1919669c81c87d6d47afd54e9.webm?t=1745518342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/a6051ac1919669c81c87d6d47afd54e9.mp4?t=1745518342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在<strong>风华浪人篇</strong>中，国际象棋遇上了推箱子。您将扮演一位浪人（皇后棋子），一路斩杀所有拦路的棋子，最终接近并消灭幕府将军。棋子的行动方式与国际象棋相同，但会像推箱子游戏那样相互推挤。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/2f6d76037cc6d21a8c43cd0d5429693b.poster.avif?t=1745518342\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/2f6d76037cc6d21a8c43cd0d5429693b.webm?t=1745518342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/2f6d76037cc6d21a8c43cd0d5429693b.mp4?t=1745518342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在<strong>足球象棋</strong>中，您将指挥棋子们进行足球比赛，如果想要突破防守并进球得分，提前考虑数步行动是重中之重。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/54f9c16a8fdde86293ec8f1c4012779c.poster.avif?t=1745518342\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/54f9c16a8fdde86293ec8f1c4012779c.webm?t=1745518342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/54f9c16a8fdde86293ec8f1c4012779c.mp4?t=1745518342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>欢迎关注我们的Bilibili官方账号HawthornGames，获取最新游戏消息及CDKey抽奖机会。QQ玩家交流群：477160979，反馈您遇到的问题及建议。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831830/extras/7880e4ce14abbbc83d32272984cd5556.avif?t=1745518342\" width=616 height=256 /></span>",
